snippet.title: Sephirothic Stories - Xbox One Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When the world tree begins to wane, what will become of the balance of the world? Discover the truth behind the world tree's waning power in a fantasy RPG!

Sephirothic Stories has arrived to Xbox One!
